snippet.title: Toy Play🎁😎 Marvin's Amazing Magic Tricks UNBOXING! Learn Magic Tricks 🎁😎Toys For Kids - Toy Team
snippet.description:
Graces teaches us how to do all the best magic tricks with Marvin's Amazing Magic Tricks! Learn how to be a master of magic with all types of tricks: cup and ball, card tricks, and more! 

➡️➡️ SUBSCRIBE to The Toy Team today for BRAND NEW videos every Wednesday & Friday: http://bit.ly/SubTTeam

Marvin's Magic were chosen to create and run the magic shops within some of the world's most prestigious stores, including Harrods in Knightsbridge, Hamleys of Regent Street in London, FAO Schwarz and the international flagship Toys R Us store in Times Square, New York. Marvin's Magic recently received Hamleys' inaugural 'Supplier of the Year' Award. Marvin's Magic has consistently been amongst their best sellers and indeed enjoyed the top spot at Christmas.

There is a lot more to magic than simply knowing how a trick is done. Your tricks are important but all good magicians take care about the way they look, move, talk and present themselves to the audience. Here are some points that will help you to become a better performer.

Many tricks require some secret preparation before they can be performed. Sometimes this may be simply to ensure that a particular object is in the correct place. At other times it can be several minutes arranging props or making a piece of apparatus. Often the preparation takes longer than the trick itself! Never let anyone see you doing this preparation or you will give away the secret. If someone asks you to do a trick and you are not ready; refuse, or do a trick that requires no preparation.

snippet.title: Lego Friends Pop Star Show Stage Set Unboxing Building Review - Kids Toys
snippet.description:
Lego Friends Pop Star Show Stage Set 41105, released mid-2015, is a cute modular set, all ready for the Lego Friends girls to roleplay being popstars with Livi! The runways can be rearranged to suit you, and there is a keyboard, electric guitar and drum kit included too. My favourite feature on this set is by far the internal workings of gears and cogs that make parts of the stage spin - this set is for older kids - and I love the incorporation of Technic pieces into the building. 

Put on a spectacular show with LEGO® Friends!

Get set for a show-stopping performance with Livi the pop star! The incredible stage is set for tonight’s concert. As the show starts, turn the stage panels to make Livi appear as if from nowhere. Set Andrea up on the drums or at the keyboard to accompany Livi for the first songs. Then it’s time for the highlight of the show—Livi sings her hit single while Andrea plays the electric guitar like a pro. Use the dancing function to see their slick dance moves! Now it’s time to rearrange the stage while Livi has a costume change before her big finale. This has been Livi’s best show yet! Includes Livi the pop star and Andrea mini-doll figures.

Includes Livi the pop star and Andrea mini-doll figures
Features a modular stage with catwalk, big screen, background panels, brick-built speakers, pop star reveal function, dancing function, drums and a keyboard set
Accessory elements include 2 fabric skirts, microphone, drumsticks and a guitar
Rearrange the different parts of the stage to create the perfect set
Turn the panels to create a magical pop star entrance
Put on the ultimate pop star spectacular with music and dance
Choose different outfits for Livi and Andrea to wear on stage

snippet.title: LEGO Friends Heartlake City Hair Salon (41391) - Toy Unboxing and Speed Build
snippet.description:
Heartlake City Hair Salon

Item: 41391
Ages: 6+
Pieces: 235

Where better to meet up with friends and share a gossip than at the salon? This toy hair styling set is brimming with scenarios for imaginative play. There’s a whole host of cute hairdressing toy salon accessories, such as toy hair dryers and toy wigs, to get imaginations sparking. With LEGO® Friends Heartlake City Hair Salon (41391) kids can role-play the client or the stylist – there's loads of crazy cuts waiting to be made. Action stations Wonderfully detailed stations allow kids to see the mini-doll figures progress through the pretend hair salon. Cute features include a shell-shaped sink, a hair-cutting chair, a styling station and a cash register. Purple bangs anyone? Instructions volumized All LEGO sets come with super-simple printed instructions, but the Heartlake City Hair Salon also features a fully enhanced building experience. Download the LEGO Life app and go to Instructions PLUS to access zoom, rotate and ‘ghost' modes. It's building for the digital age!
- Give little stylists hours of creative play with LEGO® Friends Heartlake City Hair Salon. They can pretend to cut and style their friends’ hair or imagine they are the client going to the play hair salon for a new do!
- The set is packed with features to get imaginations firing. There are 2 mini-dolls, 2 hairdressing chairs, a hair-washing sink and lots of accessories, such as toy brushes and toy wigs, to create a realistic salon experience.
- Kids will have loads of fun watching the mini-doll figure’s transformation as she progresses through the stations of the salon. And to ramp up the fun they can make over the minifigures from any other LEGO® set too!
- With 235 pieces, Heartlake City Hair Salon (41391) is an ideal gift for kids with a little building experience and a lot of imagination. It makes a great birthday, holiday or special-occasion gift for kids aged 6 and up.
- Measuring just over 4” (11cm) high and 6” (17cm) long, this play hair salon is compact enough to keep ondisplay for constant entertainment. Or kids can combine it with other LEGO® sets for truly creative play.
- No batteries are needed to power up the Heartlake City Hair Salon. The creative fun comes alive with a simple set of instructions, a little building experience and a child's active imagination.
- Is your little builder ready for an awesome play experience? Download the LEGO® Life app and help them use Instructions PLUS to see their hair salon in zoom, rotate and ‘ghost' modes. It's building for the digital age!
- Introduce little builders to the world of Heartlake City, where the girls from LEGO® Friends are waiting to accompany them on their imagination’s most exciting adventures!
- LEGO® sets meet the highest industry standards plus The LEGO Group's own quality criteria. They're consistent, compatible and connect and pull apart easily every time – it's been that way since 1958.
- LEGO® Friends sets, bricks and accessories are tested to the max to ensure that every LEGO toy playset meets the highest global safety and quality standards.

source: LEGO

LEGO© is a trademark of The LEGO Company which does not sponsor, authorize or endorse this site.

snippet.title: Lego Friends Pop Star Dressing Room Set Unboxing Building Review - Kids Toys
snippet.description:
Lego Friends Pop Star Dressing Room 41104 released mid-2015 features pop star Livi and Lego Friends Emma who comes along to style her over before her concert. I couldn't go past this set - Livi has pink and blue hair and three sparkly skirts to mix and match with. Plus her little dalmation puppy Cookie has got music notes mixed in with his spots. So very cute! The dressing room is hinged so you can set it up in all sorts of different ways. Check out the specs below and let me know what your favourite part of the set is!

Get glammed up in the foldout Pop Star Dressing Room! Livi the pop star has a big show tonight and Emma is her stylist. Help Emma choose an amazing outfit for Livi to wear on stage, then sit Livi down at the vanity desk to have her hair done. Which style and accessories will you choose tonight?

Then it’s time to relax before the performance. Fold the dressing room back to create a special doggy pampering area for Livi’s Dalmatian, Cookie. Put him in his doggy bed with a bone while Livi sits on the sofa to read some fan mail. The show is about to start, so put the finishing touches to Livi’s makeover, take a glamorous fabric skirt from the hangers and dress Livi with it. Now, she really looks like a superstar!

Includes Livi the pop star and Emma mini-doll figures, plus Cookie the Dalmatian
Folds out to create different areas with a mirrored vanity desk and clothes rail with fabric skirts
Tilting full-length mirror, sofa, opening mini-fridge element, functioning mailbox and a doggy bed
Accessories include electric blue and pink wigs, 3 fabric skirts, flowers, fan mail, fruit, bottle, magazine and a bone for Cookie
Combine with the Lego Friends Pop Star Stage (41105) to create the whole concert experience (sold separately)
279 pieces
Pop Star Dressing Room: 10 (h) x 38 (w) x 9 (d) cm

snippet.title: Jungle Magic Garden Sciencz  Unboxing and  Review Kids Toys  Kyrascope
snippet.description:
Our magical sun gives gardens and farms the light and warmth they need to grow the ingredients that go into all our favourite foods. Kyra's unboxing the super fun Jungle Magic Garden Sciencz experiment kit to show you how food grows!

Jungle Magic Garden Sciencz: Grow Your Garden, Grow Your Learning

Plants are magic. They give us oxygen to breathe, and they give us delicious food and fruits to eat.

Kyra is learning the science behind the magic with the help of her new Garden Sciencz Experimental Educational Game by Piramal Healthcare's Jungle Magic series for kids. She has donned her lab coat, and her thinking cap as she learns step by step the processes that go into planting a seed, making it sprout and nurturing it into a fully grown plant.

snippet.description:
The kids learning how to hang upside down 😂
and YOUR MERCH IS BACK!!   http://aforadley.com/

JOIN OUR FAM!! --- http://goo.gl/rfgp8V

Best Daredevil Day Ever 1155

One of the families favorite things about October is all of the Halloween decorations. Jenny, Adley and Niko Bear found some awesome bats that go perfect for the holiday and decide to hang them on the door. Adley, being the loving little girl that she is, groups them in families and names them after all of us. 

Once the door is all decorated, the find me downstairs so they can show me the great job that they did. After decorations, Adley comes up with a brand new game called statue! the rules are easy, Adley and Niko are statues, Jenny sells them, and I buy them. But they are crazy. The Adley statue moves around when I'm not looking while the Niko Bear statue has a button to make it come a live and run around the room. haha I love pretend play with the kiddos!!

With the new game done, I have to show you guys a new trick that the kiddos and I learned. We can hang from the ceiling in the kitchen!! It's hilarious, though Jenny wishes we didn't use the house like a park toy. We then head to the backyard splash pad to find some rocks for arts and crafts time.

We love doing little DIY creative projects with the kiddos, but these are extra special, because we are going to take these rocks to the construction site of a brand new LDS Temple. These temples are super important to us, so its awesome that we get to put little memories into the foundation. Adley draws pretty flowers, Niko colors his rock so good, and Jenny makes a cute rock for her and baby Navey and I make a rock about our family and how much we love each other. ( Also with a little pirate theme for pirate island lol)

After dropping of the rocks and doing some work at the lake lot, I'm home for the night! I also brought gifts for the whole family. We have A for Adley shirts again!! We have a brand new company making them and they look so good. The colors are bright, the images look great, and we are excited to share them with you guys again!! Prices are still the same, we want them to be easy for you to get. If you bought a shirt before and there were problems with it, we want to help. After unboxing the surprise, it's time to start our bed time routine and end this amazing Best Day Ever!!
